title: One climber helps another over the edge of a cliff. The climber above lies flat and extends an arm over the edge, grasping the hand of the lower climber, who hangs close to the cliff face. The.climbers and the cliff are realistic, but the background is a surreal, cubist, burning architectural tsunami against the night sky.
pid: 42335a7a-4c83-4e6b-b3c7-723f34905e4f
